bilingual.source: How did you come so far across the sea ice?
bilingual.target: 你是怎么穿过这么远的海冰来的？
这个望远镜可以看到很远的地方。

bilingual.source: We can see the mountains far away.
bilingual.target: 我们可以看到很远的山。

bilingual.source: He lives in a small town far away.
bilingual.target: 他住在一个离得远的小镇。

bilingual.source: They live in a small village far away.
bilingual.target: 他们住在一个很远的小村庄。

bilingual.source: The garden hose can spout water quite far.
bilingual.target: 花园水管可以喷出很远的水。

bilingual.source: She dreams of visiting far-off lands someday.
bilingual.target: 她梦想有一天能访问遥远的土地。

bilingual.source: Her sight is excellent; she can see very far.
bilingual.target: 她的视力非常好，可以看到很远的地方。

bilingual.source: The far-off mountains looked beautiful at sunset.
bilingual.target: 遥远的山脉在日落时看起来很美。

bilingual.source: His speech had a far-reaching impact on the audience.
bilingual.target: 他的演讲对听众产生了深远的影响。

list.abstract: FAR，A：1. 远的；遥远的；久远的；2. 较远的；那一边的；对面的；3. （政治立场）极端的。AD：1. 远；遥远地；久远地；2. 到很深的程度；到很远的距离；3. 到很大程度；很；极。N： 远方；远处
《Fár》是一部由Gunnur Martinsdóttir Schlüter执导的电影。 2023年5月27日（法国当地时间），《Fár》获第76届戛纳电影节短片特别提及。

yingyinNormal.en: Here's a drum for Danny, from a far away jungle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是给丹尼的鼓，她来自遥远的丛林。

yingyinNormal.en: Any chance any of this happened in a galaxy far, far away?
yingyinNormal.zh: 有可能这一切都是在 很远的银河发生的吗（星球大战的台词）？

yingyinNormal.en: Time to go. I must get the chronosphere back. She cannot be far away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 该走了，我一定要拿回超时空魔球，她跑不了太远的。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, Harry. Thank goodness. We'd hoped you'd only gone one grate too far.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喔，哈利！感谢老天爷，我们一直希望你只是出了比较远的炉栅。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: There has been a change. They're not coming. It's too far to walk in heels.
yingyinNormal.zh: 计划有变，她们不来了，穿高跟鞋不好走这么远的道。

yingyinNormal.en: Grandma lives there with her friend, Leo, now, and Grandpa lives far away. Sorry. I'm sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在外婆和她的朋友里奥住在那里，外公住在很远的地方。抱歉，我很抱歉。

yingyinNormal.en: Coordinates not far from Earth. If you want to know why I did what I did, go and take a look.
yingyinNormal.zh: 离地球不远的坐标，如果你想明白我做这些事的原因，去看一看。

yingyinNormal.en: He has to carry his house on his back. Doctor Hamster, I think Tiddles is escaping. He can't go far.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为他的背上背着他的房子呀。啊，仓鼠兽医，我觉得小土豆好像要逃跑。他不会走远的。

yingyinNormal.en: Are we going to the North Pole? Not quite that far, Peppa. But Father Christmas lives at the North Pole.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们是不是要到北极去呢。没那么远的佩奇。但是爸爸，圣诞老人不就是住在北极的吗。

yingyinNormal.en: Are we going to the North Pole? Not quite that far, Peppa. But Father Christmas lives at the North Pole.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们是不是要到北极去呢。没那么远的佩奇。但是爸爸，圣诞老人不就是住在北极的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Not far from the Musee du Louvre stands the Centre Pompidou, displaying the largest collection of modern art in Europe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 距离卢浮宫不远的庞毕度中心，展示全欧洲馆藏数量最多的现代艺术作品。

yingyinNormal.en: If you believed it to be impossible, I wonder you took the trouble of coming so far. To hear it contradicted, Miss Bennet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我真奇怪，你既然认为不会有这种事情 何必跑到这么远的地方来？我是想亲耳听到这则消息是假的。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, in India, when my baby brother cried like that, the servants would just take him far away so we couldn't hear it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在印度的时候，我小弟弟一哭成这德行，仆人们就会把他带到很远的地方去，这样我们就听不见了。

yingyinNormal.en: Baby Bear said, "there is a box of golden treasure at the end of the world. But it's too far for me to go because I am too little."
yingyinNormal.zh: 这时候小熊说“这个世界的尽头有一个大大的宝箱，这个箱子里面装满了金子。可是我没法去那么远的地方，因为我太小了。”

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know, Grug. We've never really walked that far. I don't think my feet can do that. I'll never live long enough to get there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不确定，瓜哥。我们从来没走过那么远的路，我觉得我的脚走不了那么远的路，我是活不到那了。

yingyinNormal.en: Dear Peppa and George, here's a present for you to share. Love from your Aunty Dottie. Aunty Dottie lives far away, in another country.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的佩奇和乔治，这是一份送给你们的礼物。爱你们的多蒂姑姑。多蒂姑姑住在很远的地方，在另一个国家。

yingyinNormal.en: Can we come too? Of course. Let's go. Are we going in an ambulance? No. The mountain's too far away. We'll go in my aeroplane. Aeroplane.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喔，我们可以跟你一起去吗？当然可以，我们走吧！我们是不是要坐救护车去？不是，山离这里有很远的的路程！我们要坐我的飞机过去！唔！飞机！唔！

yingyinNormal.en: So, what does all this have to do with time travel to the far, distant future? Well, the faster you go, the greater the effect of time dilation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么，这些和穿越时空和去遥远的未来有什么关系呢？当行驶的速度越快，时间膨胀的效应越大。

yingyinNormal.en: And for the many landlocked Chinese, traveling to far-flung seaside resorts is not an option. The answer created the world's largest artificial beach.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而对于许多居住在内陆的中国人来说，去遥远的海滨度假胜地是不现实的。这个问题催生出了世界上最大的人造沙滩。

yingyinNormal.en: Far and away the busiest part of the pit stop is the food tent. And the house specialty everyday is ginger porridge. But there are no Scottish oats here, instead it is rice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 遥远的路途上，站点中最繁忙的是食品帐篷，这些地方每天专门提供姜汤，但这里可不吃苏格兰麦片，他们喝粥。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adv. 远；遥远地；久远地；大大地；（far的比较级）

word_family.mean: adj. 远；遥远的；久远的；偏远的；极端的

examination_example.sentence: But mayors and councilors can only do so much about a problem that is <highlight>far</highlight> bigger than any one city or town.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于一个比任何一个城市都大得多的问题，市长和议员们只能做这么多。

examination_example.sentence: Just how people think is still <highlight>far</highlight> too complex to be understood, let alone reproduced, says David Eagleman, a Stanford University neuroscientist.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 斯坦福大学神经学家David Eagleman说，人们的思维方式仍然太过复杂，难以理解，更不用说复制了。

examination_example.sentence: But for the most part, these benefits seem thin, uncertain, and <highlight>far</highlight> off.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但在大多数情况下，这些好处似乎微不足道，不确定，而且遥不可及。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Far</highlight> from it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 远非如此。

examination_example.sentence: Sometimes storms blew the vessels <highlight>far</highlight> off their course, and often calm brought unbearably long delay.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有时暴风雨会把船只吹离航线，而平静往往会带来难以忍受的长时间的延误。

examination_example.sentence: And it is <highlight>far</highlight> from the only one of its type.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 而且它远不是这种类型的唯一一种。

examination_example.sentence: You're only human, and sometimes your kids can push you just a little too <highlight>far</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你只是一个人，有时候你的孩子会把你逼得太紧。

examination_example.sentence: Not surprisingly, industry groups and states generally argue it goes too <highlight>far</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不足为奇的是，行业组织和各州普遍认为它的行为太过火了。

examination_example.sentence: But too often we take this process too <highlight>far</highlight> and end up suppressing emotions, especially negative ones.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们往往把这个过程做得太过火，最终压抑情绪，尤其是负面情绪。

examination_example.sentence: Judging any given moment as well spent only in so <highlight>far</highlight> as it advances progress toward some goal.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 只有在某一时刻朝着某个目标前进时，才认为花费的时间是值得的。

word_usage.usage:
表示“遥远的”
far指空间距离远的；distant指在空间或时间上遥远的。
faraway多指距离很远的，只作定语。
remote指远离多人聚居的城镇或其他处所的。

examination_example.sentence: It was <highlight>far</highlight> from glamorous, to be honest.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 老实说，这一点也不迷人。

examination_example.sentence: So <highlight>far</highlight>, so good.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 目前为止，一切顺利。

examination_example.sentence: Why does the woman describe her experience as <highlight>far</highlight> from glamorous?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为什么这位女士将她的经历描述的一点也不迷人？

examination_example.sentence: That study found that participants who reported the highest levels of optimism were <highlight>far</highlight> more likely to live to age 85 or beyond.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该研究发现，乐观程度最高的参与者更有可能活到85岁或更老。

examination_example.sentence: Genetic differences between students are <highlight>far</highlight> greater than supposed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 学生之间的基因差异比想象的要大得多。

examination_example.sentence: Other transport must come under <highlight>far</highlight> greater scrutiny.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 其他交通工具造成的环境损害必须受到更严格的审查。

examination_example.sentence: I actually found that it was cheaper for me, as I live quite <highlight>far</highlight> away from my local supermarket.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 实际上我发现对我来说更便宜，因为我住的地方离当地的超市很远。

examination_example.sentence: With a bike, newcomers here can travel <highlight>farther</highlight> but for almost no cost.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有了自行车，新来这里的人可以走得更远，但几乎不用花钱。

examination_example.sentence: It <highlight>further</highlight> widens the gap between the old and the young.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它进一步拉大了老年人和年轻人之间的差距。

examination_example.sentence: They are <highlight>far</highlight> more curious than adults.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们远比成年人好奇。

examination_example.sentence: Often the star rating I give has <highlight>far</highlight> more to do with the kind of day I'm having.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 通常，我给的星级评级与我今天过得怎么样有很大关系。

examination_example.sentence: Now a <highlight>far</highlight> more significant motivation presents itself: meeting these goals may be necessary to prevent the collapse of our civilization.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在，一个重要得多的动机出现了：实现这些目标可能是防止我们文明崩溃的必要条件。

examination_example.sentence: The fact that such practices remain officially unaccepted reflects how <highlight>far</highlight> we haven't come from the days.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实上，这种做法仍未正式接受，这反映出，从那一天起，我们已经走了很远。

examination_example.sentence: Many of Natalie's friends had lost their homes and were living <highlight>far</highlight> away.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 娜塔莉的许多朋友失去了家园，住在很远的地方。

examination_example.sentence: Bury glass <highlight>far</highlight> away from rivers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 把玻璃埋在远离河流的地方。

examination_example.sentence: Here is a graph that charts how <highlight>far</highlight> a bird flies during the first Five days of its spring migration.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是一个图表，它描绘了一只鸟在春季迁徙的前五天飞行的距离。

examination_example.sentence: Popular beliefs regarding emotional intelligence run <highlight>far</highlight> ahead of what research can reasonably support.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 关于情商的普遍观点远远超出了现有研究可以合理支持的范围。

examination_example.sentence: I tried skateboarding there, but the locals were <highlight>far</highlight> less welcoming.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我尝试在那里玩滑板，但当地人不太欢迎我。

examination_example.sentence: Research has shown that emotional skills may contribute to some of these qualities, but most of them move <highlight>far</highlight> beyond skill-based emotional intelligence.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究表明，情感技能可能有助于其中一些品质，但其中大多数远远超出了基于技能的情商。

examination_example.sentence: How many of the things on your list have you done so <highlight>far</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 到目前为止，你已经完成了清单上的多少件事？

examination_example.sentence: For the biggest stadiums in the world, we have used data supplied by the World Atlas list so <highlight>far</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于世界上最大的体育场，我们使用了迄今为止世界地图集提供的数据。

examination_example.sentence: So <highlight>far</highlight> so good.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 目前为止一切都好。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 遥远的；恍惚的；心不在焉的；出神的

word_family.mean: adj. 远；遥远的；久远的；偏远的；极端的

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 到这种程度；到目前为止；迄今为止
与…一样远；至于；远至；一直到；就…而言
多远；到何种程度；在多大程度上

sense_info_list.zh: 遥远的; 远的; 很远

examination_example.sentence: How <highlight>far</highlight> is the bank from here?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 银行离这里有多远？

examination_example.sentence: Yongshu Island is the <highlight>farthest</highlight> island off the coast of the southern part of China.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 永潼岛是中国南部沿海最远的岛屿。

examination_example.sentence: The theater is too <highlight>far</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 剧院太远了。

examination_example.sentence: I’ve got three academic degrees so <highlight>far</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 到目前为止，我已经获得了三个学位。

examination_example.sentence: So <highlight>far</highlight>, I have won the battle!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 到目前为止，我已经赢得了这场战斗！

examination_example.sentence: The shop in Wanda Square has opened for six years, but I haven’t gone there so <highlight>far</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 万达广场的那家店已经开业六年了，但我迄今还没去过。

sense_info_list.zh: 非常; 远远; 大大

examination_example.sentence: It looks great, but it's <highlight>far</highlight> too heavy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它看起来很棒，但它太重了。

word_usage.usage:
how far表示“多远”，对距离进行提问。
如: How far is it to your house from here?
从这里到你家有多远？（牛津）
